# Pem backend (`backend/`)

**Package:** NestJS app under **`backend/`** — `npm install`, `npm run start:dev`, `npm run build` from `backend/`. No shared runtime code with `app/`.

**Stack:** **NestJS** ~11, **Drizzle ORM** + **`pg`**, **Clerk** JWT (**`jose`** + JWKS), **Svix** for `POST /webhooks/clerk`, **`@nestjs/throttler`**, **`@nestjs/swagger`** (`/docs` when not prod), **`ValidationPipe`**. **Config** — **`src/config/configuration.ts`**. **OpenAI** via **Vercel AI SDK v6** (`generateText` + `Output`, never `generateObject`). **BullMQ** + **Redis**: `dump` queue runs **extraction** after each dump. **Redis pub/sub** for **SSE** `GET /inbox/stream?dumpId=`. **Expo** push — **`notifyInboxUpdated`** (`data.kind: inbox_updated`). **No Tavily / SerpAPI / prep agents.**

**Tables:** **`users`** (incl. **`timezone`** IANA), **`dumps`** (column **`text`** — raw dump), **`thoughts`** (journal copy per dump), **`actionables`** (extracted items: tone, urgency, batch_key, dates, status), **`memory_facts`** (no `source_prep_id`).

**Layout:**

| Area | Role |
|------|------|
| `src/dumps/` | `POST /dumps`, `GET /dumps` — save dump + thought, enqueue extraction |
| `src/extraction/` | LLM extract actionables (`ExtractionService`) |
| `src/queue/dump-jobs/` | `DumpExtractService` — worker; `dump.processor` |
| `src/inbox-events/` | Redis pub/sub for inbox SSE (`InboxEventsModule` global) |
| `src/inbox/` | `GET /inbox`, `GET /inbox/all`, `GET /inbox/stream` (SSE) |
| `src/actionables/` | `GET /actionables/done`, `GET /actionables/:id`, PATCH done/dismiss/undone/undismiss/snooze |
| `src/thoughts/` | `GET /thoughts`, `GET /thoughts/:id` |
| `src/users/` | `GET /users/me`, `PATCH /users/me/timezone`, profile, push token |
| `src/profile/` | `memory_facts` CRUD for `/users/me/profile` |
| `src/push/` | Expo push |
| `src/auth/`, `src/webhooks/`, `src/health/` | unchanged patterns |

**Security:** Validate input; use **`ClerkAuthGuard`** + DB user id from JWT.

**Collaboration:** See `pem-project.mdc`.
